.TH PO-DIFF 1 "February 2026" "po-diff 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
po-diff \- compare PO/TS translation files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B po-diff
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fIOLD_FILE\fR \fINEW_FILE\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B po-diff
compares two gettext .po or Qt .ts files and shows the differences.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-f ", " \-\-format " " \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format: text (default), json, html
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output " " \fIFILE\fR
Save report to file
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version
